---
import '../../styles/tailwind.css'
import SiteHead from '../../components/SiteHead.astro'
import SiteHeader from '../../components/SiteHeader.astro'
import SiteFooter from '../../components/SiteFooter.astro'
import AnimatedBackground from '../../components/AnimatedBackground.astro'
import ArticlesSection from '../../components/ArticlesSection.astro'
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <SiteHead
    title="記事一覧 | meg+gumi"
    description="meg+gumi の記事一覧ページです。"
    canonicalPath="/articles"
    robots="noindex, nofollow"
  />
</head>
<body class="relative isolate bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100">
  <AnimatedBackground />
  <SiteHeader />
  <main class="pt-24">
    <section class="relative z-10 py-20 px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="h-0.5 w-10 bg-slate-400"></span>
          <span class="uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs text-slate-500">articles</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-slate-900">記事一覧</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-4xl text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          記事や制作メモをまとめるためのページです。いまは自作アプリと自己紹介を中心に置いています。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ArticlesSection />
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</body>
</html>
